long_desc.thetext:
from my previous experience %I64u, %I64d do not work on linux (all platforms):
  int length = sprintf(buf, " %s=\"%I64u\"", attributeName, value);
so I64 causes extra spaces

so it is easy to fix it by extra formatting manipulation:
  convert_ui64_to_string(value, strValue);
  int length = sprintf(buf, " %s=\"s\"", attributeName, strValue);

